Package ATU

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    ATUEngine
    Each ATUEngine is associated to one courseProject/request for teaming up,
    and produce one record for that courseProject
    The resultant ATU record is stored in teamList of this ATUEngine
    ATUEngine.ResultTeam
    class dedicated for showResultTable()
    CourseProject
    Each CourseProject object (e.g. comp3511_pa2) will have an associated ATUEngine to run or show output
    Act as a proxy to create/load each ATU record
    Library
    The JavaFx application that provide UI for user to perform automatic teaming up and reviewing record.
    Library.Person
    Person class for displaying table of students in the GUI
    Library.Statistics
    Statistics class for displaying Statistics table in the GUI
    Main
    Main engine of the system - where the system start
    Student
    Class for every student entity
    Each Student has SID, name, email, k1_energy, k2_energy, k3, preference and concerns.
    Team
    Class for every team entity formed after ATU.
